Asset Sales, Spinoffs Reach Half of Global Deal-Making, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-04T19:36:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/asset-sales-spinoffs-reach-half-of-global-deal-making-ft-says.html
Asset sales and spinoffs comprised
about half of global deal-making to date this year as increasing
numbers of companies attempt to streamline their operations to
boost their stock-market valuations, the Financial Times
reported, citing data from  Dealogic Holdings Plc. (DL/)   To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
